data.value:
Visual Stuido was used to create this winforms application. The Solver uses the A* search method: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A*_search_algorithm
The heuristic in this case is the combined displacement of each of the buttons. In other words, the total number of moves it would take to place each button back to it's home position without any movement restrictions.
This version of the EightPuzzle Solver does only a one-step lookahead. A more robust and accurate solver could be created using a two (or more) step lookahead algorithm.
